    <item>
      <title>信贷质量出现见顶迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/credit-quality-shows-signs-of-having-peaked-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2022 年，美联储开始以几十年来最快的速度加息后，一些美国蓝筹公司誓言开始削减债务负担。现在，这样的日子可能已经一去不复返了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/credit-quality-shows-signs-of-having-peaked-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
